        <Parent_String>gardens by location or context [300008118], gardens (open spaces) [300008090], open spaces by form [300129930], open spaces [300008072], Open Spaces and Site Elements (hierarchy name ) [300139081], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
